      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 243.037 to allow a small farm winery with a retail drink license to sell alcoholic beverages by the drink at 1 or more locations on the  licensed premises of the small farm winery without obtaining supplemental bar license."
